Psyched is a simple, fast scheduling application for planning your life.
It is task and appointment based, with fast easy operations for adding,
modifying and annotating both tasks and appointments.

Primary paradigms/features:
	Modification
		time conflicts/near conflicts
	Viewing
		simple zoom to any period
			both relative and absolute date
			paging through
		scale selection (day/3day/week)

Version	Feature
0	task (create task)
0	create appointment (unconnected to task)
1	annotate (add or edit notes on a task for item)
0	schedule task (add an appointment to a task)
		default text is the name of the task
0		schedule with date and time
0		schedule just date
0		schedule due date
	reschedule task (bring up editable list of appointments for task)

UI Modes
Schedule
	Show All
	Show Subset
Tasks
	By Due Date
